      "x": 560, "y": 950,
      "width": 320, "height": 130,
      "text": "• pf_get_task (с attachments)\n• pf_link_commit_to_task\n• pf_create_task (followup)\n• pf_write_kb_document\n\nBearer-token того же юзера,\nчто создал job",
      "originalText": "• pf_get_task (с attachments)\n• pf_link_commit_to_task\n• pf_create_task (followup)\n• pf_write_kb_document\n\nBearer-token того же юзера,\nчто создал job",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
